*Generating the order of weeks in a month
egen tsh1=max(t), by(year mth)
gen tsh2=tsh1[_n]-tsh1[_n-1]
gen wkm=1 if tsh2!=0
replace wkm=2 if wkm[_n]==.&wkm[_n-1]==1
replace wkm=3 if wkm[_n]==.&wkm[_n-1]==2
replace wkm=4 if wkm[_n]==.&wkm[_n-1]==3
tab wkm, gen(wkm)
